<div class="branchdescription">
<p>The Queen Charlotte library branch opened in 1983. Prior to this, Queen Charlotte enjoyed a community library service for many years. The location in the Community Hall was refurbished in&nbsp;2007.</p></div>
<div class="branchservices">
<div class="field field-type-content-taxonomy field-field-branchservices1">
